2020.title: 2020 Year End Review
2020.sub: 2020 was a tough year for everyone, but it was a bit more special to me. Looking back on the memorable year, I have tried to summarize what happened to me.

smartThings.title: Summer Internship Experience at SmartThings
smartThings.sub: This synthetic monitor performs as a canary for any problems that may arise in the production environment. The synthetic monitoring system measures the time of the process starting with an API call and ending with event delivery.
